h is essential for systematic processing.\n","*   **Data Consistency**: Numerical data types for odds and consistent team name representations across entries demonstrated reliable data integrity.\n","\n","### Insights or Next Steps\n","\n","*   The established multi-source aggregation and consistent data structure provide a solid foundation for implementing mechanisms to ensure lineup accuracy by enabling cross-referencing and validation of game details (teams, player names, game times) from various sources.\n","*   The next step should involve developing specific algorithms or modules that leverage this aggregated, structured data to compare and reconcile discrepancies in team names, game times, and potentially player information across sources, flagging any inconsistencies for review to guarantee high lineup accuracy.\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"83bdb7dd","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773763937725,"user_tz":240,"elapsed":43,"user":{"displayName":"garry evans","userId":"18049878967172356456"}},"outputId":"d8fdc4e1-3258-4868-b148-4b2bc76ccce6"},"source":["nba_df.info()"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["<class 'pandas.core.frame.DataFrame'>\n","RangeIndex: 6 entries, 0 to 5\n","Data columns (total 11 columns):\n"," #   Column            Non-Null Count  Dtype  \n","---  ------            --------------  -----  \n"," 0   game_id           6 non-null      object \n"," 1   home_team         6 non-null      object \n"," 2   away_team         6 non-null      object \n"," 3   source            6 non-null      object \n"," 4   money_line_home   6 non-null      int64  \n"," 5   money_line_away   6 non-null      int64  \n"," 6   spread_home       6 non-null      float64\n"," 7   spread_home_odds  6 non-null      int64  \n"," 8   spread_away       6 non-null      float64\n"," 9   spread_away_odds  6 non-null      int64  \n"," 10  requested_game    6 non