0151"},"source":["## Create placeholder app.py\n","\n","### Subtask:\n","Create a minimal `app.py` file that includes a `build_sports_engine` function and a placeholder for `TeamFormPlugin` to enable task progression.\n"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"3d78ada3"},"source":["**Reasoning**:\n","The previous attempts to locate and execute `app.py` failed because the file was not present. To progress with the task, a placeholder `app.py` needs to be created in the environment as instructed by the subtask. This code block will generate the content for the `app.py` file and then write it to disk.\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"a18d7817","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773351962975,"user_tz":240,"elapsed":68,"user":{"displayName":"garry evans","userId":"18049878967172356456"}},"outputId":"37bfc234-2b84-4d29-d87f-7a9f7a41ab8a"},"source":["%%writefile app.py\n","import streamlit as st\n","import time\n","\n","# Placeholder for TeamFormPlugin\n","class TeamFormPlugin:\n","    def __init__(self, name=\"Mock TeamFormPlugin\"):\n","        self.name = name\n","    def get_form_data(self, team_name):\n","        # Return some mock form data\n","        return {\"team\": team_name, \"form\": [1, 0, 1, 1, 0]}\n","\n","# Placeholder for build_sports_engine function\n","def build_sports_engine(plugins=None):\n","    if plugins is None:\n","        plugins = []\n","\n","    # Simulate prediction data generation\n","    mlb_predictions = [\n","        {\"game_id\": \"mlb_1\", \"home_team\": \"Yankees\", \"away_team\": \"Red Sox\", \"prop\": \"Total Bases\", \"player\": \"Aaron Judge\", \"prediction\": 1.5, \"confidence\": 0.75},\n","        {\"game_id\": \"mlb_2\", \"home_team\": \"Dodgers\", \"away_team\": \"Giants\", \"prop\": \"Strikeouts\", \"player\": \"Clayton Kershaw\", \"prediction\": 6.5, \"confidence\": 0.82}\n","    ]\n","    nfl_predictions = [\n","        {\"game_id\": \"nfl_1\", \"home