ct structure and completeness of information for each component of the parlay."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"5f9f8dd9"},"source":["## Analyze Parlay Predictions\n","\n","The analysis of the generated parlay predictions confirms that the `build_parlay` function correctly combines individual prediction legs, calculates combined American odds, and determines an overall confidence score.\n","\n","### Parlay 1: Pistons Money Line + Joel Embiid Points Over 28.5\n","*   **Combined American Odds**: `191`\n","*   **Overall Confidence**: `31.30%`\n","*   **Legs Verification**:\n","    *   **Pistons Money Line**:\n","        *   `description`: \"Pistons Money Line\"\n","        *   `predicted_outcome`: \"Pistons\"\n","        *   `predicted_confidence`: `61.28%`\n","        *   `odds`: `-180`\n","        *   **Structure**: Correctly contains all required fields.\n","    *   **Joel Embiid Points Over 28.5**:\n","        *   `description`: \"Joel Embiid Points Over 28.5\"\n","        *   `predicted_outcome`: \"Over 28.5\"\n","        *   `predicted_confidence`: `51.08%`\n","        *   `odds`: `-115`\n","        *   **Structure**: Correctly contains all required fields.\n","\n","### Parlay 2: Suns Money Line + Tyrese Haliburton Assists Over 9.5\n","*   **Combined American Odds**: `214`\n","*   **Overall Confidence**: `29.07%`\n","*   **Legs Verification**:\n","    *   **Suns Money Line**:\n","        *   `description`: \"Suns Money Line\"\n","        *   `predicted_outcome`: \"Suns\"\n","        *   `predicted_confidence`: `55.73%`\n","        *   `odds`: `-140`\n","        *   **Structure**: Correctly contains all required fields.\n","    *   **Tyrese Haliburton Assists Over 9.5**:\n","        *   `description`: \"Tyrese Haliburton Assists Over 9.5\"\n","        *   `predicted_outcome`: \"Over 9.5\"\n","        *   `predicted_confidence`: `52.17%`\n","        *   `odds`: `-120`\n","        *   **Structure**: Correctly contains all required fields.\n","\n","### Ov